WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.766 --> 00:00:02.000
This is too much.

2
00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:03.433
How can they be so ungrateful?

3
00:00:03.933 --> 00:00:06.500
Since His Majesty woke up,

4
00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:08.433
you haven’t visited him at all.

5
00:00:08.466 --> 00:00:10.000
Isn’t that inappropriate?

6
00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:12.133
I wouldn’t mention that ungrateful emperor.

7
00:00:12.133 --> 00:00:13.866
But just thinking about it makes me furious.

8
00:00:15.100 --> 00:00:17.666
Are you going to the Yangxin Hall?

9
00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:28.800
Ah.

10
00:00:29.533 --> 00:00:32.000
It seems there’s no hope of leaving the palace.

11
00:00:32.766 --> 00:00:33.566
Ah.

12
00:00:34.700 --> 00:00:37.000
His Majesty needs to take his medicine.

13
00:00:44.466 --> 00:00:47.366
Has Consort Rong visited the Yangxin Hall recently?

14
00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:52.100
Doesn't he know that I’m suffering inside?

15
00:00:52.866 --> 00:00:54.166
Has it been raging like this?

16
00:00:54.166 --> 00:00:57.600
Uh, maybe recently,

17
00:00:57.600 --> 00:01:00.100
the Consort has been exhausted from taking care of His Majesty.

18
00:01:00.166 --> 00:01:03.066
She must be very tired.

19
00:01:03.100 --> 00:01:06.300
The Consort is certainly worried about His Majesty as well.

20
00:01:06.600 --> 00:01:11.333
Perhaps she’s also unable to sleep, thinking about him.

21
00:01:11.333 --> 00:01:12.666
Is it that serious?

22
00:01:13.066 --> 00:01:15.200
Then I’ll go and see her.

23
00:01:21.066 --> 00:01:22.400
What’s going on?

24
00:01:47.100 --> 00:01:48.466
Ah.

25
00:01:50.566 --> 00:01:52.500
What happened? Continue the music.

26
00:01:52.700 --> 00:01:55.000
Continue, Your Highness.

27
00:01:55.366 --> 00:01:57.266
What’s wrong with the Consort?

28
00:01:58.300 --> 00:02:00.400
Get up quickly.
